Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.99,0:20:10.54,ED2CHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}总觉得…这样可以吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.76,0:20:14.14,ED2CHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}「你和我很合得来呢」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.57,0:20:21.96,ED2CHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}不约而同地想要彼此相见  同步率好高哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.20,0:20:25.67,ED2CHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}怎样的问候语才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.98,0:20:29.40,ED2CHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}「你注意到了吗？」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.77,0:20:36.12,ED2CHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}一边轻声说出来  一边挥着小手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.80,0:20:44.27,ED2CHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}想要让这样的每一天都持续下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.02,0:20:50.78,ED2CHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}就把茶匙扔出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.72,0:20:59.76,ED2CHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}掌管咖啡的神仙啊  总有一天我们会长大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.85,0:21:07.24,ED2CHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}用白色的牛奶来  描绘出大家的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.90,0:21:14.99,ED2CHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}掌管咖啡的神仙啊  总有一天我们会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.13,0:21:19.71,ED2CHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}成为可爱的大人…虽然是这么打算的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.80,0:21:25.40,ED2CHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}不过接下来的事情可就不知道咯！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,----------TXT----------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.78,0:00:12.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我给大家看去露营时候的照片哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.95,0:00:15.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你拍了这么多照片啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.84,0:00:17.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.48,0:00:19.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拍的很棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.31,0:00:21.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是我妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.44,0:00:23.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是你拍的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.17,0:00:27.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个美丽的姑娘是谁呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.74,0:00:29.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.92,0:00:30.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是心爱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.04,0:00:31.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.20,0:00:34.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的没看出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.45,0:00:35.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.64,0:00:36.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Me？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.66,0:00:37.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也太惊讶了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.82,0:00:40.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实看起来比较成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.26,0:00:43.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次我可以拿走一张吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.82,0:00:45.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智乃很有才能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.53,0:00:46.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是一张奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.32,0:00:49.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  连你们也…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.94,0:02:23.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智乃  这是照相机吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.83,0:02:26.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露营时开始拍照之后就上瘾了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.26,0:02:29.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以让我好好拍拍你们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.28,0:02:31.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在拍照吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.83,0:02:33.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主题是  平时的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.93,0:02:35.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像往常一样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.22,0:02:38.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被这么说反倒觉得有点难了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.92,0:02:39.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智乃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.12,0:02:43.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摆姿势更有趣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.51,0:02:47.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  我感到了很厉害的温度差
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.84,0:02:51.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我拍一下你们在说话时的样子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.30,0:02:53.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.65,0:02:54.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.30,0:03:02.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你总来捣乱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.45,0:03:06.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶  我只是在工作却被批评了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.76,0:03:08.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个照片好有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.46,0:03:11.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那这种的怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.53,0:03:13.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平时的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.46,0:03:18.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跳的好累
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.10,0:03:20.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.38,0:03:22.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  不能一直这样偷懒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.22,0:03:24.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.19,0:03:28.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也来给我拍张照
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.80,0:03:30.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.12,0:03:33.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很老练
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.44,0:03:35.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天做了保养
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.63,0:03:40.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为心爱的影响  目的已经开始跑偏了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.62,0:03:43.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很有野性啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.45,0:03:45.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拍专注于拍照的智乃…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.53,0:03:49.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不知道背后有人照她…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.36,0:03:51.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姐的背影…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.40,0:03:55.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最佳镜头
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.69,0:03:56.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.98,0:03:58.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么最佳镜头啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.53,0:04:02.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  要到打工的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.18,0:04:03.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纱路  你没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.69,0:04:08.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近我总是会忘记时间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.95,0:04:09.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纱路
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.04,0:04:11.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.33,0:04:13.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.53,0:04:16.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么会知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.49,0:04:18.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心爱让她跑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.36,0:04:19.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.01,0:04:21.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明只差一点了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.34,0:04:23.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.37,0:04:25.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么那么执着于平时的样子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.12,0:04:28.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还专门把照相机带到店里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.50,0:04:32.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是在隐瞒什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.62,0:04:34.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来告诉姐姐们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.85,0:04:39.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊  被拍了奇怪的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.00,0:04:43.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然一下子就能摆出表情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.37,0:04:42.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18}求删…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.22,0:04:46.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多要开始打扫店里了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.72,0:04:47.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.45,0:04:50.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢乐的露营也结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.42,0:04:52.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要回归为一名劳动者啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.11,0:04:55.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好意思说自己劳动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.93,0:04:58.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千夜要不要再喝一杯咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.77,0:05:01.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呀  恭敬不如从命啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:02.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.40,0:05:04.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.11,0:05:07.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里夹了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.32,0:05:09.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是探宝游戏的地图
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.97,0:05:11.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好怀念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.68,0:05:15.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是要找到宝物然后把其中一样和自己的交换
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.95,0:05:19.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18}对对  结束后是要把地图藏在别的地方对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.35,0:05:18.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,探宝游戏？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.36,0:05:23.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不知道小镇上到底藏着多少地图
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.40,0:05:25.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以前找到过好多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.98,0:05:26.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.16,0:05:29.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只和纱路找过一点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.34,0:05:34.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这个小镇上…大家都玩过啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.64,0:05:36.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想玩…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.93,0:05:41.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们下次一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.48,0:05:42.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶  可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.28,0:05:43.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.25,0:05:47.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以把麻耶和惠叫来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.14,0:05:48.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.50,0:05:50.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我作为姐姐会努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.65,0:05:59.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家  宝物都带过来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.84,0:06:01.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇者的断剑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.46,0:06:03.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像宝石一样的扣子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.57,0:06:05.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遇难船只的瓶装船模
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.61,0:06:06.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不错啊不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.94,0:06:09.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论哪个都能激起人的冒险欲望呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.01,0:06:11.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.30,0:06:12.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你带了什么过来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.37,0:06:17.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用提比掉的毛做的提比分身
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.60,0:06:18.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最没用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.03,0:06:19.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.26,0:06:25.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理世也来就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.52,0:06:28.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为她今天留下来看店所以今天才能过来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.40,0:06:31.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那还要感谢理世呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.51,0:06:35.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我虽然是第一次但是会努力引领大家前进的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.64,0:06:37.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可靠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.32,0:06:40.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还没有找到过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.24,0:06:41.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.68,0:06:45.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得最开始是刚上初中的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.11,0:06:49.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对对  就是那次遇到了智乃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.79,0:06:59.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  下一位  开始自我介绍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.00,0:07:04.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  我是香风智乃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.10,0:07:07.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将来的梦想是成为出色的咖啡师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.20,0:07:12.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻耶  咖啡师是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.10,0:07:16.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我在游戏和电影里见过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.81,0:07:18.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那个把箭和石头之类打出去的兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.93,0:07:19.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.94,0:07:22.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是想打破人生的墙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.57,0:07:28.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来好酷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.90,0:07:31.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是个很厉害的咖啡师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.24,0:07:36.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  你来成为我们的同伴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.19,0:07:39.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才我们找到了探宝游戏的地图
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.66,0:07:42.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么突然干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.65,0:07:44.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们需要咖啡师的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.00,0:07:46.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可是重要的战斗力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.54,0:07:50.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智乃加入到了队伍中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.51,0:07:55.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有过这种事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.14,0:07:57.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我第一次听说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.58,0:07:59.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自从那时开始关系就很好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.87,0:08:02.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个奇怪的误会真是抱歉呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.88,0:08:06.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那次的探宝游戏那么难吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.24,0:08:08.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.20,0:08:11.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻耶立马开始绕路走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.04,0:08:14.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惠提议玩其他游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.49,0:08:17.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智乃说已经累了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.32,0:08:19.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底赖谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.67,0:08:20.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赖谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.01,0:08:22.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.16,0:08:25.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这次没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.47,0:08:27.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有姐姐在哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.71,0:08:30.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心爱你是个路痴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.57,0:08:31.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.07,0:08:34.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好好看这个地图就能到达的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.47,0:08:36.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这些图全都拼凑起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.37,0:08:40.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃  从而能够得出的答案是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.95,0:08:45.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王冠  兔子  店
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.64,0:08:47.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.09,0:08:50.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是有名的帽子店…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.68,0:08:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.65,0:08:54.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是让在甘兔庵吃豆沙水果凉粉是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.93,0:08:56.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害  不愧是心爱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.16,0:08:59.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般人想不出这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.18,0:09:00.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.57,0:09:02.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只是想吃豆沙水果凉粉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.36,0:09:07.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要证明心爱的想法是有多么的肤浅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.10,0:09:13.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们用一下秘密的通道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.26,0:09:15.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边更近哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.22,0:09:18.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是在冒险一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.50,0:09:21.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是以前寻宝的时候发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.83,0:09:24.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候被叶子封着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.68,0:09:27.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是近路但是过不去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.94,0:09:30.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易来了一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.80,0:09:32.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里到了智乃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.45,0:09:33.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出场的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.11,0:09:36.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是咖啡师的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.28,0:09:45.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.21,0:09:47.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智乃你还有那种能力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.80,0:09:48.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是他们捏造的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.25,0:09:52.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以为在遇到我之前你还会那种魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.60,0:09:56.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咖啡师是泡咖啡的职业啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.31,0:10:01.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻耶她们总是乱说  很脱线
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.34,0:10:08.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个小镇真漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.73,0:10:09.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.31,0:10:13.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽是些想让人绕路的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.32,0:10:15.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.33,0:10:19.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绕道的话就可以多玩会儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.66,0:10:26.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许她们俩刚和智乃见面的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.63,0:10:30.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是想让关系变得更好所以总是脱线呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.14,0:10:31.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.27,0:10:49.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心爱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.55,0:10:53.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这次想大家一起找到宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.70,0:10:54.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.94,0:10:57.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智乃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.95,0:10:59.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智乃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.58,0:11:01.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感觉公园那边有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.54,0:11:04.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两个人都别偷懒了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.87,0:11:06.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好努力找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.63,0:11:16.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心爱也快来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.55,0:11:17.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.32,0:11:24.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  这个是不是智乃说的帽子店的牌子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.53,0:11:28.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在盆栽箱的后面找到了一个宝箱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.20,0:11:30.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智乃好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.77,0:11:33.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  打开吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.92,0:11:34.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.81,0:11:35.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.48,0:11:40.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  你们还记得咱们是怎么走到这里的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.80,0:11:42.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们去热爱了许多的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.05,0:11:44.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又稍微憎恨一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.42,0:11:48.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铭刻着灵魂的回忆和羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.10,0:11:51.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是  宝物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.61,0:11:54.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,侧面有个新的地图贴在上面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.53,0:11:55.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.74,0:11:57.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说怎么这么奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.77,0:11:59.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是知道的哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.49,0:12:01.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是故意那么说的！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.10,0:12:07.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据地图
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.48,0:12:10.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貌似在这个小洞的尽头有着宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.11,0:12:13.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有小孩才进得去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.88,0:12:17.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.44,0:12:19.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勉勉强强能进来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.94,0:12:20.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轻松轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.99,0:12:23.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心爱不会进不来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.06,0:12:28.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里只有被选中的霍比特人才能通过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.34,0:12:31.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就在这里和提比阻止追兵！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.28,0:12:32.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.76,0:12:36.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18}妹妹们啊  踩着我的尸体前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.64,0:12:33.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玩得真开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.29,0:12:35.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.81,0:12:43.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个神圣的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.29,0:12:45.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宝箱就藏着这里的某处
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.97,0:12:48.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就…就是这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.27,0:12:50.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.14,0:12:51.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.09,0:12:54.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是荣誉勋章！好帅气
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.69,0:12:57.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来有不少人来过这里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.83,0:13:00.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有…甘兔庵的打折券？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.93,0:13:02.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连捶肩券都有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.76,0:13:02.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs18}甘兔庵  9折优惠券
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.76,0:13:02.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs18}捶肩券  请珍惜地使用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.38,0:13:06.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们三个  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.66,0:13:07.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是不快点回去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.14,0:13:09.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心爱就会一直在那里等着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.06,0:13:11.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,STOP
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.02,0:13:16.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次的寻宝比以前的都要开心吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.62,0:13:18.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为心爱在的缘故吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.76,0:13:21.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有点吃醋了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.69,0:13:24.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对是你们的错觉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.32,0:13:27.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是霍比特一族的休息之地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.78,0:13:28.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.62,0:13:32.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就算身体这么大  内心还是小小的！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.50,0:13:35.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,内心小小的不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.10,0:13:38.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明心爱也变成霍比特人就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.36,0:13:42.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果心爱还是没能完成呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.82,0:13:46.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,规则上能动宝箱的只有设置宝箱的本人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.69,0:13:48.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于那个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.19,0:13:50.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有个好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.05,0:13:52.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.78,0:14:01.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还想再一次寻宝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.94,0:14:05.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过会儿跟智乃商量下好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.61,0:14:38.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智乃会不会同意我的请求呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.32,0:14:42.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智乃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.99,0:14:47.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大部分的都是有趣的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.86,0:14:50.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是为什么一有跟心爱扯上关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.82,0:14:53.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她因为生气身子都在颤抖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.18,0:14:56.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智乃…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.94,0:14:58.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心…心爱！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.09,0:15:03.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我的错拍出来的都是那种照片
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.31,0:15:04.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.84,0:15:06.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没在生气啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.78,0:15:09.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智乃理想中的姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.19,0:15:11.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这只吧？！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.82,0:15:13.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只不就是心爱么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.38,0:15:15.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.74,0:15:19.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然那张照片上的心爱的确看起来很有姐姐范
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.91,0:15:20.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.32,0:15:22.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想说的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.88,0:15:24.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还不够格呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.98,0:15:29.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全没能成为合格的智乃的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.47,0:15:34.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能够像照片这样更加像个成熟的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.94,0:15:38.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能成为让智乃引以为傲的姐姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.12,0:15:42.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的我…就连让智乃感到自豪都不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.47,0:15:45.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.46,0:15:49.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  智乃…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.47,0:15:55.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我一直觉得心爱来到这个小镇真的是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.15,0:15:57.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心爱你这个大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.81,0:16:00.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真…真敢扔啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.72,0:16:04.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么一直都这么自作主张地下定论…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.28,0:16:11.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.38,0:16:13.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很疼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.88,0:16:14.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是因为这个哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.27,0:16:18.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…你不是在哭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.09,0:16:21.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.13,0:16:23.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不告诉你呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.76,0:16:25.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.62,0:16:28.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃我一枕头！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.21,0:16:33.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚有点喧嚣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.99,0:16:38.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛这种程度比起安安静静的好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.41,0:16:39.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我意外地都习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.34,0:16:42.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照这么下去还不得上房揭瓦总有一天会把店给拆了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.72,0:16:43.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说啥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.14,0:16:45.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我店闹拆了我就困扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.73,0:16:47.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也给我加把劲去让生意更加兴隆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.15,0:16:51.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是把「有着会说话的兔子的有趣咖啡店」作为卖点的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.66,0:16:52.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会更有反响也说不定哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.15,0:16:55.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的明白老夫的心情吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.23,0:16:58.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦…那个是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.71,0:17:01.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…不能看！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.51,0:17:05.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐写给智乃的信？！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.21,0:17:11.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「实际上  只要是心爱寄给我的照片就都是搞笑风格的」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.31,0:17:14.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「所以想麻烦你多发点普通的日常照…」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.76,0:17:17.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为  为什么要瞒着我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.63,0:17:19.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果让你知道这是给摩卡姐的照片的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.99,0:17:22.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你肯定会去做酷酷的动作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.29,0:17:23.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会？！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.58,0:17:25.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是一直都是自然的哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.82,0:17:27.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是已经介意得不行了吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.47,0:17:43.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个东西准备好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.71,0:17:44.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备OK的说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.42,0:17:47.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们会不会高兴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.86,0:17:58.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,探宝游戏的地图？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.66,0:18:01.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新的宝物由初中生组藏好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.33,0:18:04.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的这个可是难度很高哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.83,0:18:08.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有…这个打折券能用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.35,0:18:10.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.24,0:18:17.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…是我努力做出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.84,0:18:19.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请收下它！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.54,0:18:20.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情书？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.92,0:18:24.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心爱  理世  请把这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.61,0:18:26.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.96,0:18:29.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为之前看店的谢礼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.57,0:18:31.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们几个藏起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.97,0:18:34.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次轮到我来看店
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.51,0:18:35.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两位也去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.00,0:18:37.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是针对我们的挑战状呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.22,0:18:40.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前只有我没有通过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.07,0:18:42.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我接受了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.82,0:18:44.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.90,0:18:50.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.20,0:18:56.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈  快看快看  寄过来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.06,0:18:59.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.82,0:19:01.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心爱和智乃寄来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.79,0:19:12.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不错的照片哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.77,0:19:14.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智乃  谢谢你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.67,0:19:16.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看上去很精神  妈妈我也就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.99,0:19:19.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  这个…是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.20,0:19:21.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你的妹妹哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.93,0:19:22.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.90,0:19:24.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,My sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.46,0:19:29.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也看看心爱的好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.86,0:19:33.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她也迟迟不回家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.47,0:19:36.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然的话  我可就要再回去见见她咯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.49,0:19:41.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然呢  心爱送过来的照片全都很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.29,0:19:43.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我也很喜欢这种的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.62,0:19:46.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐  好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.07,0:19:48.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过的还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.55,0:19:51.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有个重要的通知要跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.67,0:19:52.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.58,0:19:56.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为姐姐瞒着我要抢走智乃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.87,0:19:59.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我一个月内不会跟姐姐联系
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.84,0:20:03.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明没那个打算的！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.06,0:20:05.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心爱啊！！！！！！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.17,0:21:43.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么大家  把得到的宝物拿出来看看！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.47,0:21:47.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个勋章…是我从小到大一直在收集的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.83,0:21:50.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然  我就觉得理世肯定会选这个的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.13,0:21:52.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是麻耶放进去的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.19,0:21:55.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的是  芭蕾舞鞋的钥匙圈哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.15,0:21:56.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.15,0:22:00.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是希望你一直都能华丽地舞动起来的护身符哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.68,0:22:04.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就像芭蕾舞者那样一直骨碌骨碌地迎客好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.26,0:22:07.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个让人静不下心来的咖啡店呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.54,0:22:10.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的是这个可爱的小小的书哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.11,0:22:15.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.43,0:22:17.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是青山小姐放进去的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.71,0:22:19.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又能再跟大家一起玩了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.23,0:22:22.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太好了呢  纱路
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.60,0:22:25.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又来了…真是让人没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.77,0:22:26.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心爱的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.10,0:22:29.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个奇怪的脸的人的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.93,0:22:31.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…不就是你么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.08,0:22:32.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Me？！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.99,0:22:37.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个就是…我就是宝物的意思吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.05,0:22:38.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不对  智乃…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.88,0:22:51.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是…不把店再弄热闹点的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.50,0:23:00.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都交给姐姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.47,0:23:02.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.42,0:23:05.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦…心爱？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.18,0:23:07.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…我睡着了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.24,0:23:09.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.61,0:23:11.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感觉好像听到了什么话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.69,0:23:14.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么都没有说哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.70,0:23:16.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心爱  听我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.27,0:23:17.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才纱路她…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.42,0:23:18.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.69,0:23:19.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理  理世学姐？！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.43,0:23:22.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  那个不都是怪千夜吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.29,0:23:22.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.99,0:23:26.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明在和小惠她们喝红茶呢  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.16,0:23:27.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对呀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.34,0:23:29.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智乃要不要吃点饼干？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.69,0:23:32.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唔…我开动了哦
